  "body": "{\"subject\":\"BTNHResurrection is out! ;-)\",\"template\":{\"name\":\"albumOut\",\"data\":{\"intro\":\"It's a special moment for me today! I'm so exited to share with you my last project that I released today!\",\"image\":\"http://music-2068.kxcdn.com/MediumStorage/wvsHpLhcvAyva36wg-mediumFile_Bone_Thugs_n_Harmony_Flesh_n_Bone_Is_Home_A_Documentary_Film.jpg\",\"album\":\"BTNHResurrection\",\"message\":\"We are working of this track since a long time. The track is very positive because we wanned to inspire people in their every day challenges! I played the piano and Jimmy the bass. Josh have made a wonderful job on the arrangement sending us right back to the 70's. We are really proud of it! I hope that you will love it.\"}}}",
